  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t土匪中国伪“刑法” 擦屁股纸内第243条 “<b>妄笑罪</b>”：<br/>\r\n…<br/>\r\n243.1条。<b>该笑却不笑罪：</b><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/6455\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/6455\">领袖发表重要历史性讲话</a>时必须笑而鼓掌磕头流泪欢呼；<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58426\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58426\">瞻仰领袖圣物</a>时必须涕泗横流大笑致敬呼万岁望山仰止；<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/55206\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/55206\">拜见领袖美国亲密朋友战友玩弄女人幼童</a>时需亲密微笑；<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/57954\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/57954\">参观历史博物馆等重要战略宫殿要地</a>等需始终笑容如一；<br/>\r\n…<br/>\n<br/>\r\n243.2条。<b>不该笑却笑罪：</b><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58396\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58396\">闻狗与作风硬打胜仗擅笑失声</a>；<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58448\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58448\">购买祖国世界首发明科技产品</a>；<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/57255\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/57255\">遇床管城管等祖国政府职员时</a>；<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/57002\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/57002\">聆听市委书记讲话布置任务时</a>；<br/>\r\n…<br/>\n<br/>\r\n243.3条。<b>妄笑罪刑罚量刑：</b><br/>\r\n一般妄笑十年有期徒刑；<br/>\r\n情节严重认罪态度恶劣可判无期；<br/>\r\n态度特别恶劣死不悔改者<b>死刑</b>！<br/>\n<br/>\r\n参见：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/56497\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/56497\"><b>中华人民共和国放屁法</b></a><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\"><b>乱世笑林</b></a> </div>",
